        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Hope Opportunity and Prosperity for Everyone Act or the Hope Act</b></p> <p>This bill (1) limits assistance under the Temporary Assistance for Needy Families (TANF) program; (2) restricts eligibility for participation in the Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program (SNAP); and (3) otherwise revises provisions related to TANF and SNAP, including with respect to work requirements.</p>]]></text>
